de.hunsicker.jalopy

Class Jalopy.State

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hunsicker.jalopy.Jalopy.State
  • Enclosing class:
    Jalopy

    public static final class Jalopy.State
extends Object
    Represents a Jalopy run state. You may want to use Jalopy.getState() to query the engine about its current state.
    Since:
    1.0b8
